{
  "stem": "8703.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I, being a presser, you know, for some times, I had an idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was-- he was calling various machinists and various mechanics and everything, and they couldn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I, I showed him-- and he was present over there, that murder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he saw me, that I have an idea, even with the presses that are going very low.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they don't compress as they supposed to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I still-- I didn't want to stay away, because if they-- if we didn't work, if we didn't have any work, they send us to various works which was even worse.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was bad, but we were used to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were not used to carry very heavy grenades like my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was used to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- so we did something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I showed him that we can still work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cannot-- I told him, we cannot produce the quota.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a certain amount, we can still produce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since then, he knew that he beat me up so badly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He put me in charge of the-- of the production, of the quality of production.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had it much easier that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to go around and check if the production-- I was-- I was responsible for the quality of production.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If there was something wrong, he warned me, you're going to be responsible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if something was wrong, they were accusing of sabotage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw to it, well, it was my job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I checked and everything else if-- if the production is all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once it was-- when we used to go to work, a foreman from our division, a Polish man, came to the barracks, the camp, and he took us to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He brought us to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
